 = [[A Taste of Hope]]\n|tradeable = No\n|placeholder = Yes\n|equipable = No\n|stackable = No\n|noteable = No\n|options = Read\n|destroy = Drop\n|examine = A tatty old diary.\n|value = 1\n|weight = 0.510\n|id = 22411\n}}\n[[File:Old diary detail.png|left|130px]]\nThe '''old diary''' is obtained during [[A Taste of Hope]] by searching the bed next to the staircase in Serafina's home.\n\nWritten by Serafina's brother, the diary describes [[Ranis Drakan]] and [[The Maiden of Sugadinti|Serafina]] making a deal to cure her brother of his illness, which players find out later in the quest was transforming him into the [[abomination]]. The same story, but from Serafina's perspective, can be read in [[Serafina's diary|her diary]].\n\nIf lost, it can be reclaimed from Serafina's home or from a [[bookcase]] within a [[player-owned house]].\n[[File:A Taste of Hope - Route to Serafina's home.png|thumb|left|The route to Serafina's home, where the old diary can be found.]]\n==Transcript==\n{{Hastranscript|Old diary|transclude=Yes}}\n\n{{A Taste of Hope}}"}